longBusinessSummary: Precomp Solutions AB (publ) manufactures and supplies precision components and cutting tools in Europe. It offers components in various types of material using fineblanking technology; produces deep drawned components using stamping technology; offers manual and semi-automated assembly solutions; and designs and manufactures tools. Precomp Solutions AB (publ) was founded in 1956 and is headquartered in Ulricehamn, Sweden.
